00:14:20.960 --> 00:14:24.740
it's like a champagne bottle--
just the cork comes out,

00:14:24.740 --> 00:14:26.270
and the bubbles
fly out, and it's

00:14:26.270 --> 00:14:27.900
like excitement in the air.

00:14:27.900 --> 00:14:31.010
He's just funny, and
laughing, and goofing.

00:14:31.010 --> 00:14:34.340
And yeah, when he and Ivan
get together it's nonstop.

